'''cycloid''' (''plural'' '''cycloids''')
#{{geometry}} The [[locus]] of a [[point]] on the [[circumference]] of a [[circle]] that [[roll]]s without [[slip]]ping on a fixed [[straight]] [[line]].
#{{zoology}} A [[fish]] having cycloid [[scale]]s.

